SUBSTITUTE N (Â§TH N) TARGET N IF (p (V <TH-Acc-Any><RO-Ess-Any>))(0 Acc)(*0 Ess BARRIER GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY)(NEGATE 0 Â§TH) ;
SUBSTITUTE Pron (Â§TH Pron) TARGET Pron IF (p (V <TH-Acc-Any><RO-Ess-Any>))(0 Acc)(*0 Ess BARRIER GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY)(NEGATE 0 Â§TH) ;
SUBSTITUTE Num (Â§TH Num) TARGET Num IF (p (V <TH-Acc-Any><RO-Ess-Any>))(0 Acc)(*0 Ess BARRIER GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY)(NEGATE 0 Â§TH) ;

