	##
SUBSTITUTE Pron (Â§RE Pron) TARGET Pron IF (p (V <RE-Acc-Ani>))(0 Acc)(NEGATE 0 Â§RE) ;

SUBSTITUTE N (Â§RE N) TARGET N IF (p (V <RE-Ill-Ani><TH-Acc-*Ani>) OR (V <TH-Acc-Any><RE-Ill-Any>))(0 Ill)(s Acc)(NEGATE 0 Â§RE) ;

SUBSTITUTE Pron (Â§RE Pron) TARGET Pron IF (p (V <RE-Ill-Ani><TH-Acc-*Ani>) OR (V <TH-Acc-Any><RE-Ill-Any>))(0 Ill)(s Acc)(NEGATE 0 Â§RE) ;
	## SÃĄmediggi liiko go SÃĄmi ealÃĄhusrÃĄÄÄi addÃĄ doarjaga nissoniidda mat ÃĄlggahit ealÃĄhusdoaimma.

SUBSTITUTE N (Â§RE N) TARGET N IF (p (V <RE-Ill-Ani>))(0 Ill)(NEGATE 0 Â§RE) ;
SUBSTITUTE Pron (Â§RE Pron) TARGET Pron IF (p (V <RE-Ill-Ani>))(0 Ill)(NEGATE 0 Â§RE) ;

	# "map" CO-Agent role
	# --------------------


SUBSTITUTE N (Â§CO N) TARGET N IF (p (V <CO-Acc-Ani>))(0 Acc + Sem/Animate)(NEGATE 0 Â§CO) ;
	## Diehttelas boazu liiko varas, ruona ÅĄattuide juste seamma lÃĄdje go mii olbmot liikojit varas lÃĄibÃĄi.

SUBSTITUTE N (Â§CO N) TARGET N IF (p (V <CO-Com-Ani>))(0 Com + Sem/Animate)(NEGATE 0 Â§CO) ;
