SUBSTITUTE N (Â§XT N) TARGET N IF (*0 (V <XT-Com-Measure>) BARRIER GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY1 OR GRAMCHK-VFIN)(0 Com OR (Pl Loc))(NEGATE 0 Â§XT) ; ;
