SUBSTITUTE N (Â§OR N) TARGET N IF (p (V <TH-Acc-Any><OR-Loc-Any>)) (0 Loc)(s Acc OR Gen)(NEGATE 0 Â§OR) ;
SUBSTITUTE Pron (Â§OR Pron) TARGET Pron IF (p (V <TH-Acc-Any><OR-Loc-Any>)) (0 Loc)(s Acc OR Gen)(NEGATE 0 Â§OR) ;


	# "map" ATTRIBUTE role
