ADD:real-GenSg-NomSg (&real-GenSg-NomSg) TARGET Ã-A-E-O-U-NOUNS + CONC-2-3-4ABC - <spelled> - Prop - Err/Orth IF (0 (N Sg Acc) - PxSg2 OR (N Sg Gen) - PxSg2)(-1 GRADE-ADV - ("oba") - ("vel") LINK -1 COPULAS)(NEGATE 0 Der/vuota)(NEGATE 0 (A Sg Nom) OR (A Attr) OR Ess)(NEGATE 1 N OR Po OR Actio)(NEGATE *1 TV BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE);
	#$ Mis lea gal juo mÃĄtki diÅgojuvvon ja mÃĄkson, muhto jus mannÃĄ bures ekonomalaÄÄat dÃĄppe, de besset mÃĄnÃĄt oassÃĄlastit doaimmaide gos soitet vel {oahpu} ge gazzat, nu go historjjÃĄlaÅĄ bÃĄikkiid oaidnit, ja nu ain.
	#$ ja mariidna bioteknologiija olis, de lea dÃĄrbu ahte stÃĄhta searvÃĄ ovddidan- ja ÃĄlggahandÃĄsis nana ruhtademiin DjO-doaimmaide ja earÃĄ doaimmaide, main Davvi-Norggas leat erenoamÃĄÅĄ {luonddu} addin lihkostuvvanovdamunit.
