ADD:real-jÃĄmas (&real-jÃĄmas) TARGET ("japmat" Der/st) OR ("japma" N Sg) IF (0 VGen OR (Imprt Sg2) OR (ImprtConNeg) OR (Prs ConNeg) OR (Acc PxSg3) OR (Gen PxSg3) OR Loc)(-1 GRADE-ADV) ;
ADD:real-jÃĄmas (&real-jÃĄmas) TARGET ("japmat" Der/st) OR ("japma" N Sg) IF (0 VGen OR (Imprt Sg2) OR (ImprtConNeg) OR (Prs ConNeg) OR (Acc PxSg3) OR (Gen PxSg3) OR Loc)(-1 BE) ;

