ADD:real-jÃĄmas (&real-jÃĄmas) TARGET ("japmat" Der/st) OR ("japma" N Sg) IF (-1 (N Acc) LINK *-1 JAMAS-VERB OR <jÃĄmas> BARRIER NPNHA LINK 0 TV) ;
