COPY:lex-transitive ("ovdÃĄnahttit" TV SUGGEST) EXCEPT ("ovdÃĄnit" IV &lex-transitive) OR ("ovdÃĄnit" IV Err/Orth-a-ÃĄ &lex-transitive) BEFORE V-MOOD OR Inf TARGET ("ovdÃĄnit" IV &lex-transitive) ;
COPY:lex-transitive ("rievdadit" TV SUGGEST) EXCEPT ("rievdat" IV &lex-transitive) OR ("rievdat" IV Err/Orth-a-ÃĄ &lex-transitive) BEFORE V-MOOD OR Inf TARGET ("rievdat" IV &lex-transitive) ;
