ADDRELATION:msyn-acc-to-adv (RIGHT $2) (Num &msyn-acc-to-adv) TO (*1 &msyn-acc-to-adv + ACC-ADV);
    
ADD:xmsyn-acc-to-velggolaÅĄ (&msyn-acc-to-velggolaÅĄ) TARGET Num IF (NOT 0 ACC-NUM-ATTR OR Acc LINK 1 CURRENCY OR Sem/Money LINK 1 ("velggolaÅĄ")) ;  #2nd
