ADD:msyn-numphrase-sgnom (&msyn-numphrase-sgnom) TARGET ("akta" Sg Nom) OR ("1" Sg Nom) IF (*1 PRE-NP-HEAD BARRIER NOT-ADV LINK 1 CC LINK 1 PRE-NP-HEAD LINK *1 (N Sg Nom) + &msyn-numphrase-sgnom BARRIER NOT-Attr - PrfPrc - GRADE-ADV  - (A <AttrPred> Sg Nom) - (A <AttrPred> Sg Gen) - (A <AttrPred> Sg Acc) - (Pcle Foc/Neg-ge) - (Pcle Foc/Pos-ge) OR JAHKASAS LINK NOT 0 (N Coll Nom) OR ("tuvsÃĄn" Num Pl Nom)) # OR PL-PAIR-N) 
