#DELETE SECOND ROUND
		
ADD:xpunct-rihkku (&punct-rihkku) TARGET BUT-CC + CC IF (NEGATE -1 COMMA OR BOS OR QMARK OR (";") OR ("âĶ") OR (":") OR ("-"));	
	#$ Undertittel: {Muhto} Heaika ii bala dien âsÃĄnisâ.
    #$ Jus vÃĄssÃĄnÃĄigi livÄÄe earÃĄlÃĄgan, de livÄÄe maid min dÃĄlÃĄÃĄigi ja boahtteÃĄigi earÃĄlÃĄgan âĶ Muhto ÃĄllet fal divtte ovttage dadjat didjiide ahte lea menddo maÅÅit!	
